video.title: Duck Dynasty: Collection
video.synopsis: Follow the ups and downs of life for the Robertsons, who created a business empire in the Louisiana bayou with their line of duck calls and decoys.

episodes.synopsis: Jase, Si and the guys from the call room eat to compete at a donut shop, and Si wins a prize; Willie gets roped into shopping with Phil and Ms. Kay.
episodes.title: Of Mattresses and Men

episodes.synopsis: When Willie pushes his work force too far, the guys go on strike; Ms. Kay decides to take her home cooking to the streets with her own food truck.
episodes.title: Duck No, We Won't Go

episodes.synopsis: On the eve of Duck Season, the men differ over comforts on their traditional camp-out; Phil hopes for some loving from Ms. Kay, yet refuses to bathe.
episodes.title: Duck Season Eve

episodes.synopsis: Thinking their wives are now "too city," Willie and Jase invite Korie and Missy on a deer hunt; Ms. Kay sifts through her junk to find a treasure.
episodes.title: Let's Go Hunting, Deer

episodes.synopsis: The Duck Commander team unveils a wing of the Bass Pro shop; featuring their products; Ms. Kay tries to get some quality time in with her grandkids.
episodes.title: Bass Man Standing

episodes.synopsis: When Sadie visits Duck Commander for a school project, the guys test one of Jase's inventions; Phil and Jep take Priscilla and Meritt to a horse farm.
episodes.title: The Big LeCOWski

episodes.synopsis: Jase concludes that Willie is having a mid-life crisis; the Robertson brothers vie to see who is most fit; Phil and Kay have a mouse problem.
episodes.title: Battle of the Brothers

episodes.synopsis: Everyone comes together to plan a surprise wedding for Phil and Kay, as Si disracts the couple by taking them on a personal trip down memory lane.
episodes.title: Til Duck Do Us Part

episodes.synopsis: Due to a termite problem, the guys are forced to work from Godwin's house; Ms. Kay gets Korie and Willie to help with her Golden 60's club.
episodes.title: Termite Be a Problem

episodes.synopsis: The guys have to work all night to catch up, but Jase and Willie abandon them for another mission; Phil scares Mia and Priscilla with a ghost story.
episodes.title: From Duck 'Til Dawn
